O zaman daha çok ağla.” “Bacakların kısa olduğu için şişko tavşan.” “Seni aldım. Bu yüzden artık bana aitsin.” Bu… bu normal değil~!!! Kara panterler yetmezmiş gibi bir de aslanlar ve kurtlar ortaya çıkmaya başladı. Onca yer varken yırtıcı yaratıkların toplanma yeri olmak zorunda mıydı? column23:
ko:"무공에 미친 사내 광마 이자하.
그가 미치기 전의 평범했던 시절로 돌아왔다.

세상에 광마로 알려진 이자하.
그는 마교 교주의 보물인 천옥을
column24: 주인인 교주가 마음에 들지 않는다는 이유로 훔친다.\n이어지는 마교의 추적.\n이자하는 몇 날 며칠 쫓아오는 수많은 마교 정예들을 처단했지만 결국 막다른 길에 몰려 더는 도주할 수 없게 되고
column25: \n추적자들과 교주에게 엿을 먹이기 위해 죽기 전에 천옥을 집어삼키고 장렬하게 마지막 싸움을 치른 뒤 벼랑에 떨어지게 되는데
column26:
눈을 떠보니 모두에게 무시당하던 자하객잔의 점소이 시절로 돌아와 있다.
과거로 돌아온 그의 머릿속엔 이 상황에 대한 의문점보다는 다른 생각이 들어찬다.
‘더 강해질 수 있다!’
한 번 걸어간 길이고 무공에 대한 이해가 높으니 광마 시절보다 더 강해질 수 있다는 사실뿐.
주변 상황 파악보다는 자신의 몸 상태를 살피고 내공 심법부터 돌리는 이자하.
그걸 마친 후에나 상황을 살펴보니 자신이 최근 말도 안 되는 누명으로 두들겨 맞고 객잔은 박살 나 있던 때라는 걸 알게 된다.
과거 모두에게 무시당하며 살던 평범한 점소이가 아닌 무림을 오시하던 광마 이자하로 뒤바뀐 상황.
그는 어떤 행보를 이어갈 것인가!

column40: the older sister of Asterion in the novel

you're alive! Have you gotten younger?"

She started spouting more puzzling things

Lyrica is a hardworking 8-year-old girl who has always used her vivid imagination to escape the harsh realities of living in the slums with her neglectful mother. After her mother has a premonition of a disastrous future

column25:

column28: description:{"en":"It’s been many years since I’ve bloodied my hands for the United Empire and its emperor
column29:
Ragnar. I wanted to return to my hometown and live a quiet life as if to repent for my sins. However–

“You are a great 8th class magician who is able to overthrow me and the empire at any time. How could I let a monster like you stay alive?”

After being betrayed on the verge of death by Ragnar
column30: who was my friend as well as my Emperor
column31:
he stabbed my heart with a dagger that had time magic applied to it.

“The penance I want is to put everything back to its place.”

---
As a powerful 8th class mage
column32: Ian Paige took countless innocent lives under the orders of Emperor Ragnar
column33: a close friend and ruler of the Greenriver Empire. Yet despite their closeness
column34: Ragnar views Ian as a threat and subsequently poisons him. Using time magic
column35: Ian saves himself and returns 30 years to the past. Now a young boy
column36: Ian joins an elite order of mages to hone his abilities once again. This time
column37:
he’ll get revenge on the emperor who betrayed him and reclaim glory as an 8th class mage!

column13: description:{"en":"The boy Leopin was born with unnaturally high dexterity. From an early age
column14: he used his dexterity to contribute to his peers in a variety of crafts. Leopin and his friends entered the Royal Pioneer Academy. However
column15: during the “Ritual of Ability Development” at the entrance ceremony
column16:
the status given to Leopin was disastrous.

“Occupation: Unemployed.”

“All statuses except dexterity remain at their initial values and do not grow.”

“Skill is dextrous master of none”

Leopin’s classmates exiled him because he had nothing to offer other than his dexterity. Leopin is placed in the “Special Training Class”
column17: a class for failures. Leopin is left all alone. However
column18: he realizes that the skill he has been given
column20:
” has an unexpected performance. That is…

You can convert your dexterity status to any other status.
You can change your occupation to any one you want.

The first thing Leopin did was to become a lumberjack. First
column21: Leopin changed his job to “Lumberjack” to get wood from the forest. He then became a carpenter and built the most magnificent house of all. He became an Appraiser to identify rare items
column22: and a Battle Axe User to fight off students from other classes who tried to attack him. Become a Ranger to explore dungeons and a Ninja to get through traps with ease.\n\nLeopin
column24: had gained enough power to do everything.\n\nAs Leopin continues to be a warrior
column25: he is adored by his childhood friend
column27: and admired by a beautiful alchemist
column28: and his activities become even more well known. On the other hand
column29: the classmates who expelled Leopin regret their decision to do so when they witness Leopin’s abilities.\n\nTheir home remains a shack
column31: and they gradually lose their place in the school and are ruined.\n\n*Explanation: the skill is not “poor dexterity”
column33: which is the Japanese equivalent to a Jack of all trades
column34: master of none; since they can do a bit of everything
column36: but since they have mastered none
column37: they supposedly cannot make a living from it
column38: hence they are “poor”.  Another manner of saying you have high dexterity is to be \"handy\"
column39: back-translated from DEX as in *manual* dexterity from early RPGs.  \"An unemployed handyman who does a bit of everything\" just doesn't quite roll off the tongue."}

column49: zh:"剑尊大战魔尊后同归于尽！\n百年后竟重生成柔弱孩童？\n男主清明前世是闻名江湖的华山派梅花剑尊，耗尽全力消灭了武林魔头“天魔”，最终与其同归于尽。但他却在百年后重生成了一个落魄小乞丐，并且保留着前世所有记忆。而在现世，曾是江湖名派的“华山派”已经没落至无人知晓的地步，清明得知这一事实后不能接受。当他找到华山后，发现门派已油尽灯枯。但清明仍然还记得百年前门派的道义和武学精神，他很不甘心，于是以孩童之身重新拜入华山派门下。但入门后他才知道，原来门派没落竟与前世自己和天魔大战有关！孩童之身的他该如何重振门派雄风呢？"
column50: zh-hk:"華山派梅花劍尊青明與天魔同歸於盡後，再次醒來發現百年後的華山派竟已不屬於九派一幫，震驚之下他立志要讓華山派重振當年盛極一時的威風!"}
